name: CityLiquor
0:
”Alexa, ask city liquor what is the deal of the day”
”Alexa, ask city liquor to find me some coupons”
”Alexa, ask city liquor to give me guidance”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: city liquor
Developer Terms of Use
des:
You can ask City Liquor for any coupons or deals. For example you can
- ask "city liquor what is the deal of the day" or 
- ask "city liquor to find me some coupons" or
- ask "city liquor for any deals" or 
- ask "city liquor for any coupons"
- ask "city liquor for help"
